{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position, then weigh cauliflower and broccoli into it. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>12-15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until al dente. Set Varoma aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place flour, butter, milk, wine, salt and pepper into mixing bowl and cook <b>7 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>.","Add ground nutmeg (optional) and 150 g of the Danish blue cheese and mix <b>1 min\/speed 5<b>. Adjust seasoning to taste.","Preheat oven grill to a high setting. Transfer cooked cauliflower and broccoli into a round casserole dish (23 cm), then cover with cheese sauce in mixing bowl. Sprinkle remaining 50 g of the Danish blue cheese over the top, then place under the grill for approx. 10-12 minutes, or until cheese is golden brown. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","500 g cauliflower, cut into florets","500 g broccoli, cut into florets","50 g plain flour","40 g butter","500 g full cream milk","40 g dry white wine","½ tsp sea salt, to taste","2 pinches ground white pepper,  to taste","1 - 2 pinches ground nutmeg              (optional)","200 g Danish blue cheese, cut into pieces (2-3 cm)"]}],"id":"r89820","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-smMY3X5wdB0\/XZVPma3SD9I\/AAAAAAAAc6o\/_e1KapcQzSowo9JQpJyKryVtBdpLuYHUQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ABDH7ajnrCJD5DmG.png","title":"Cauliflower, broccoli and blue cheese gratin","publishedAt":"2015-12-14T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"16 g","fat":"20 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13 g","calories":"1279 kJ \/ 304 kcal"},"usefulItems":"round casserole dish (23 cm), oven grill","hintsAndTricks":["Vegetables that are cooked al dente are tender but still firm to the bite."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","6 portions"]}